SIRNAME (surname / title)

Syntax: sirname <word>

At level 10 and above, you may request a permanent surname (last name or
honorific) to be appended to your character name.  This is a one-time
permanent change.

Requirements:
  - Level 10 or higher
  - Alphabetic letters only (no numbers, spaces, or punctuation)
  - Cannot be changed once set

The surname appears after your character name in all places where your
name is shown to others.  Choose carefully.

Example:
  sirname Ironhide
  Your name would then appear as: Thurtea Ironhide

Note: Rifts characters with a sirname skip the standard Nightmare title
progression.  Your OCC title continues to reflect your level separately.

See also: score
